# 
# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/accessTypeConcept
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/accessTypeConcept> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/accessTypeConcept> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/idsa/core/Resource> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/accessTypeConcept> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/accessTypeConcept> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a resource to a SKOS concept describing its access mode (e.g., 'download', 'compute-in-place'). Replaces the deprecated :accessType string property."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/accessTypeConcept> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Vincula un recurso con un concepto SKOS que describe su modo de acceso (p. ej., 'descarga', 'cómputo-in-situ'). Reemplaza la propiedad string obsoleta :accessType."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/accessTypeConcept> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "access type (concept)"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/accessTypeConcept> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tipo de acceso (concepto)"@es .
# 
# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/appliesToFeatureConcept
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/appliesToFeatureConcept> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/appliesToFeatureConcept> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Metric> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/appliesToFeatureConcept> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/appliesToFeatureConcept> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a metric to a formal schema element (as a SKOS Concept) describing the feature/column it applies to. Use this when a formal schema definition exists. For simple JSONPath strings, the deprecated :appliesToFeature (string) may still be used."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/appliesToFeatureConcept> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Vincula una métrica con un elemento de esquema formal (como un Concepto SKOS) que describe la característica/columna a la que aplica. Use esto cuando exista una definición de esquema formal. Para strings JSONPath simples, aún puede usarse la obsoleta :appliesToFeature (string)."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/appliesToFeatureConcept> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "applies to feature (concept)"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/appliesToFeatureConcept> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "se aplica a característica (concepto)"@es .
# 
# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/conformsToProfile
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/conformsToProfile> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/conformsToProfile> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/conformsTo> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/conformsToProfile> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Distribution> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/conformsToProfile> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataProfile> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/conformsToProfile> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a distribution/representation to a DataProfile that describes its structure and characteristics. In IDSA/DCAT, technical profiles are associated with the concrete delivery form (Distribution), not the abstract product (Resource)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/conformsToProfile> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Vincula una distribución/representación con un DataProfile que describe su estructura y características. En IDSA/DCAT, los perfiles técnicos se asocian con la forma concreta de entrega (Distribution), no con el producto abstracto (Resource)."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/conformsToProfile> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "conforms to profile"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/conformsToProfile> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "se ajusta al perfil"@es .
# 
# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/conformsToSchema
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/conformsToSchema> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/conformsToSchema> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/conformsTo> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/conformsToSchema> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataProfile> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/conformsToSchema> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a profile to a formal technical schema (e.g., JSON Schema, XSD, SQL DDL). Unlike the (semantic) profile, the schema defines the exact physical structure."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/conformsToSchema> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Vincula un perfil con un esquema técnico formal (p. ej., JSON Schema, XSD, SQL DDL). A diferencia del perfil (semántico), el esquema define la estructura física exacta."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/conformsToSchema> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "conforms to schema"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/conformsToSchema> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "se ajusta al esquema"@es .
