<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/metricType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a Metric measurement to a standardized MetricType definition from the controlled vocabulary. Aligned with dqv:isMeasurementOf for DQV interoperability."@en .
