<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/usesVocabulary> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "DEPRECATED: Use :hasMetricStandard instead. Links a profile or a metric to a concept scheme (controlled vocabulary) that defines the allowed values for the data (e.g., a SIEX or AGROVOC thesaurus). Useful for categorical columns."@en .
