<http://purl.org/dc/terms/Frequency> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A rate at which something recurs. Used for dct:accrualPeriodicity (DCAT-AP 3.0)."@en .
<http://purl.org/dc/terms/Frequency> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Una tasa a la que algo se repite. Usado para dct:accrualPeriodicity (DCAT-AP 3.0)."@es .
