# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataAsset
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataAsset> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataAsset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/idsa/core/DataResource> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataAsset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Bridge class for a data asset. Specialises ids:DataResource to add the EDAA domain-specific semantic description (e.g., servesObservableProperty). Can be linked to the DataApp that generated it using prov:wasGeneratedBy. In v0.4.0+, profiles are linked via ids:representation → dcat:Distribution → :conformsToProfile, not directly on the DataAsset."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataAsset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Clase puente para un activo de datos. Especializa ids:DataResource para añadir la descripción semántica específica del dominio EDAA (p. ej., servesObservableProperty). Puede vincularse a la DataApp que lo generó usando prov:wasGeneratedBy. En v0.4.0+, los perfiles se vinculan mediante ids:representation → dcat:Distribution → :conformsToProfile, no directamente en el DataAsset."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataAsset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Activo de Datos"@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataAsset> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Data Asset"@en .
