<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataProfile> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Bolsa de facetas que describe las características de los datos (dominio, tipo, propiedades observadas, CRS, geometría, resolución espacial/temporal).\n    \nPropiedades típicas:\n• dcat:temporalResolution: granularidad temporal (xsd:duration, p. ej., P1D)\n• dcat:spatialResolutionInMeters o InDegrees: granularidad espacial (xsd:decimal)\n• :declaresObservedProperty: variables semánticas de esquemas de conceptos\n• :declaresDataClass: clasificación de tipo de datos\n• :hasCRS: sistema de referencia de coordenadas (IRI)\n\nAlineado con W3C DCAT 3 para interoperabilidad de catalogación de conjuntos de datos."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataProfile> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Facet bag describing data characteristics (domain, type, observed properties, CRS, geometry, spatial/temporal resolution).\n    \nTypical properties:\n• dcat:temporalResolution: temporal granularity (xsd:duration, e.g., P1D)\n• dcat:spatialResolutionInMeters or InDegrees: spatial granularity (xsd:decimal)\n• :declaresObservedProperty: semantic variables from concept schemes\n• :declaresDataClass: data type classification\n• :hasCRS: coordinate reference system (IRI)\n\nAligned with W3C DCAT 3 for dataset cataloguing interoperability."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataProfile> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Data Profile"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataProfile> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Perfil de Datos"@es .
# 
# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataRepresentation
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataRepresentation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataRepresentation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/idsa/core/DataRepresentation> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataRepresentation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Physical representation of (structured) data. Specializes ids:DataRepresentation \n    from the IDSA taxonomy to add EDAAnOWL-specific semantics for data profiles and quality metrics.\n    \n    Alignment: ids:DataRepresentation extends dcat:Distribution (W3C DCAT 2+), \n    ensuring interoperability with DCAT-based catalogs while maintaining IDSA compliance."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataRepresentation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Representación física de datos (estructurados). Especializa ids:DataRepresentation \n    de la taxonomía IDSA para añadir semántica específica de EDAAnOWL para perfiles de datos y métricas de calidad.\n    \n    Alineación: ids:DataRepresentation extiende dcat:Distribution (W3C DCAT 2+), \n    asegurando interoperabilidad con catálogos basados en DCAT mientras mantiene conformidad IDSA."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataRepresentation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Data Representation"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/DataRepresentation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Representación de Datos"@es .
# 
# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Metric
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Metric> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Metric> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dqv#QualityMeasurement> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Metric> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> _:genid22 .
