<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Metric> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A class representing a single, measurable characteristic (measurement) of an asset or profile. Aligned with dqv:QualityMeasurement. Use :metricType to link to the standardized metric definition (dqv:Metric)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Metric> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Una clase que representa una característica única y medible (medición) de un activo o perfil. Alineada con dqv:QualityMeasurement. Use :metricType para vincular a la definición de métrica estandarizada (dqv:Metric)."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Metric> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Metric (Measurement)"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Metric> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Métrica (Medición)"@es .
# 
# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/MetricType
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/MetricType> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/MetricType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dqv#Metric> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/MetricType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A controlled vocabulary term for standardized metric definitions (e.g., completeness, recordCount, cloudCoverage). Aligned with dqv:Metric. RECOMMENDED: Use external vocabularies like DDI (SummaryStatisticType), STATO (Statistical Methods Ontology), or W3C DQV for quality metrics. Use :metricType to link a measurement (:Metric) to its definition."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/MetricType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un término de vocabulario controlado para definiciones de métricas estandarizadas (p. ej., completitud, recuento de registros, cobertura de nubes). Alineado con dqv:Metric. RECOMENDADO: Usar vocabularios externos como DDI (SummaryStatisticType), STATO (Statistical Methods Ontology) o W3C DQV para métricas de calidad. Use :metricType para vincular una medición (:Metric) con su definición."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/MetricType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Definición de Métrica (Tipo)"@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/MetricType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Metric Definition (Type)"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/ObservableProperty
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/ObservableProperty> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/ObservableProperty> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/ObservableProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/ObservableProperty> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "La variable semántica que describe un activo de datos o que un servicio requiere/produce. RECOMENDADO: Usar AGROVOC para conceptos agrícolas o EuroSciVoc para ciencia general."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/ObservableProperty> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The semantic variable that a data asset describes or a service requires/produces. RECOMMENDED: Use AGROVOC for agricultural concepts or EuroSciVoc for general science."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/ObservableProperty> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Observable Property"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/ObservableProperty> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Propiedad Observable"@es .
# 
# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/PerformanceMetric
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/PerformanceMetric> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/PerformanceMetric> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Metric> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/PerformanceMetric> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A metric that describes the performance of a DataApp or service (e.g., accuracy, execution time)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/PerformanceMetric> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Una métrica que describe el rendimiento de una DataApp o servicio (p. ej., precisión, tiempo de ejecución)."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/PerformanceMetric> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Métrica de Rendimiento"@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/PerformanceMetric> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Performance Metric"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/PredictionApp
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/PredictionApp> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/PredictionApp> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/idsa/core/SmartDataApp> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/PredictionApp> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A smart data app that produces predictions/inferences from input data using a model or algorithm."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/PredictionApp> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Una aplicación de datos inteligente que produce predicciones/inferencias a partir de datos de entrada usando un modelo o algoritmo."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/PredictionApp> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Aplicación de Predicción"@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/PredictionApp> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Prediction App"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityMetric
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityMetric> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityMetric> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dqv#QualityMetric> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityMetric> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Metric> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityMetric> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A metric that describes a qualitative or quantitative aspect of data quality (e.g., completeness, uniqueness, record count). Aligned with dqv:QualityMetric."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityMetric> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Una métrica que describe un aspecto cualitativo o cuantitativo de la calidad de datos (p. ej., completitud, unicidad, recuento de registros). Alineada con dqv:QualityMetric."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityMetric> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Métrica de Calidad"@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityMetric> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Quality Metric"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityReport
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityReport> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityReport> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A class representing an external, structured quality report, containing metadata about the assessment (e.g., a PDF report URL, a quality score)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityReport> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A structured report containing quality metrics and metadata."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityReport> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Un informe estructurado que contiene métricas de calidad y metadatos."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityReport> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Una clase que representa un informe de calidad externo y estructurado, que contiene metadatos sobre la evaluación (p. ej., una URL de informe PDF, una puntuación de calidad)."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityReport> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "External Quality Report"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityReport> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Informe de Calidad"@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityReport> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Informe de Calidad Externo"@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityReport> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Quality Report"@en .
