<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Uniqueness> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/QualityMetric> .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Uniqueness> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Metric representing the degree to which data values are unique."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Uniqueness> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Métrica que representa el grado en que los valores de los datos son únicos."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Uniqueness> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Unicidad"@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/Uniqueness> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Uniqueness"@en .
