<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasCRS> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Deprecated. Use the object property edaan:hasCRS to link to a formal CRS definition."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasCRS> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a Data Profile to the formal definition of its Coordinate Reference System (CRS), preferably using an EPSG URI (e.g., http://www.opengis.net/def/crs/EPSG/0/4326). Range is skos:Concept for interoperability with controlled vocabularies."@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasCRS> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Obsoleto. Use la propiedad de objeto edaan:hasCRS para vincular a una definición formal de CRS."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasCRS> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Vincula un Perfil de Datos con la definición formal de su Sistema de Referencia de Coordenadas (CRS), preferiblemente usando un URI EPSG (p. ej., http://www.opengis.net/def/crs/EPSG/0/4326). El rango es skos:Concept para interoperabilidad con vocabularios controlados."@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasCRS> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "CRS de perfil (IRI)"@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasCRS> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has Coordinate Reference System"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasCRS> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "profile CRS (IRI)"@en .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasCRS> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "tiene Sistema de Referencia de Coordenadas"@es .
<https://w3id.org/EDAAnOWL/hasCRS> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#deprecated> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
